{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 2: The Q&A system is given a text and starting topic ('obesity').",
    "It starts by automatically asking the causes and consequences of obesity.",
    "Results are parsed to extract topics and the type of causation.",
    "Once obesity is covered, the system follows-up on each topic at distance 1 (starting with 'physical activity'), then at distance 2, and so on.",
    "The maximum distance can be user-defined."
  ]
}